data.description: Looking for your dream home in North Charleston, South Carolina? Look no further! Introducing 7672 Brandywine Road, a charming gem that ticks all the boxes! This amazing three-bedroom, one-bathroom home is nestled on a quiet street with a spacious lot, perfect for privacy and tranquility. What makes this home even more enticing? Besides stainless-Steel Appliances, it comes with a brand-new roof, installed just two years ago, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Say goodbye to gutter maintenance headaches, as this home boasts oversize gutters with leaf guard technology, new hot water heater, enjoy the new fencing surrounding the rear of the property.  Step inside and prepare to be wowed! This home features updated internal features, adding a modern touch.Welcome Home to Pepperhill!
